gn: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-722403e7-7fff-cea9-0db3-a64d7d28250f"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Пенальти к попаданию</span></span></div>\r\n\t\t\t</th>\r\n\t\t\t<th scope="col" style="border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;">\r\n\t\t\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-722403e7-7fff-cea9-0db3-a64d7d28250f"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Последствия серьезного ранения</span></span></div>\r\n\t\t\t</th>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t</thead>\r\n\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t<tr style="height:0pt">\r\n\t\t\t<td style="border-left:solid #000000 1pt;border-right:solid #000000 1pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1pt;border-top:solid #000000 1pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;">\r\n\t\t\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-722403e7-7fff-cea9-0db3-a64d7d28250f"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">4 или меньше</span></span></div>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style="border-left:solid #000000 1pt;border-right:solid #000000 1pt;border-bottom: